      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE COMES BILLY (6) finished fifth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 425m at this track, taking a Grade 5 in a dynamic 23.77. Has the ability and looks hard to top. PAW KRISTELLE (1) shapes well for this after winning last start over the 400m at Warragul in a dynamic 22.56. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. LET IT LINGER (2) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Finished second (23.56) at Horsham last time making it three minors on end. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to be in this for a long way. DOONGALLA NOMES (3) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a neck second (17.11) in a Grade 5 at Healesville.",
